    recent versions of some installed programs (i.e. firefox, fsarchiver,
    gparted, ntfs-3g, testdisk/photorec, thunderbird).
  * Updated X option to install Flash Player for FireFOX etc.

NOTE: There's a GRUB2 version of RIPLinuX, the difference is it uses
      GRUB2 to boot the ISO, instead of ISOLinux, if one doesn't
      boot you can try the other. The PXE version is self explanatory
      to those who would be interested.

